content: This is fine, but I don't quite understand your request.  By the way, I can only pass onto the [content created by volunteers](https://app.reach.vote/library/gallery/c07cfbbe-ed31-4770-8303-833364ba39b8?campaign=democrats) gallery by the Content Brigade.
Changed the channel name: request for Content Created by Volunteers

My request was that the folder for LGBTQ+ content be updated. None of the ones in there are wrong, and they're all semi relevant, but there's not a lot of newer content to share about what the race looks like for LGBTQ people now. Maybe we add some graphics or videos of quotes from Harris and Walz, like more content from when Harris visited the RuPaul set or content about Walz being the head of the G/S alliance? It's only a suggestion!
Oh and some facts about Harris performing gay marriages would work too!

Sorry, that's the LGBTQ+ Democratic Coalition's gallery.  (The Content Brigade only has the [content created by volunteers](https://app.reach.vote/library/gallery/c07cfbbe-ed31-4770-8303-833364ba39b8?campaign=democrats) gallery.)  You can ask if Out For Harris-Walz controls the LGBTQ+ gallery.
Gotcha! Thank you for trying to help me!
You're welcome!  [Out For Harris](https://events.democrats.org/event/671143/) has an upcoming Organizing call.
